@base = {{host}}/api
@token = {{token}}
@myCommentId = 1

### 1) 评论成功（预期 code=0）
POST {{base}}/comment/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "postId": 1,
  "replyToCommentId": null,
  "replyToUserId": null,
  "content": "这是第一条评论",
  "imageUrl": null
}

### 2) 未登录评论（预期 code=406）
POST {{base}}/comment/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "postId": 1,
  "replyToCommentId": null,
  "replyToUserId": null,
  "content": "未登录评论",
  "imageUrl": null
}

### 3) 参数非法（预期 code=422）
POST {{base}}/comment/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "postId": null,
  "replyToCommentId": null,
  "replyToUserId": null,
  "content": "",
  "imageUrl": null
}

### 4) 目标帖子不存在（预期 code=409）
POST {{base}}/comment/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "postId": 999999,
  "replyToCommentId": null,
  "replyToUserId": null,
  "content": "目标帖子不存在",
  "imageUrl": null
}

### 5) 公开评论分页（预期 code=0）
GET {{base}}/comment/page?postId=1&pageNum=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6) 评论分页参数非法（预期 code=422）
GET {{base}}/comment/page?postId=1&pageNum=0&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7) 我的评论分页（预期 code=0）
GET {{base}}/comment/my/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8) 删除我的评论成功（预期 code=0）
POST {{base}}/comment/delete/{{myCommentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9) 删除不存在评论（预期 code=410）
POST {{base}}/comment/delete/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10) 删除他人评论（预期 code=412，需准备他人评论ID）
POST {{base}}/comment/delete/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
